<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 02:27:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普同意与伊朗停火</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/on-the-eve-of-destruction-clock-ticks-down-on-trumps-iran-deadline</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普正在放弃终结伊朗的威胁，因为伊朗文明的基础是霍尔木兹海峡的迅速开放。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/on-the-eve-of-destruction-clock-ticks-down-on-trumps-iran-deadline"&gt;特朗普同意与伊朗停火的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/on-the-eve-of-destruction-clock-ticks-down-on-trumps-iran-deadline</guid></item><item><title>大型 RQ-180 隐形无人机飞越希腊的新视角</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/new-views-of-massive-rq-180-stealth-drone-flying-over-greece</link><description>&lt;p&gt;人们继续发现这架秘密无人机在白天飞行，为人们对其功能提供了新的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/new-views-of-massive-rq-180-stealth-drone-flying-over-greece"&gt;大型 RQ-180 隐形无人机飞越希腊的新观点&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 23:30:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/new-views-of-massive-rq-180-stealth-drone-flying-over-greece</guid></item><item><title>A-10 疣猪正在接受空中加油探针测试（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe</link><description>&lt;p&gt;除了 A-10 的胜利之外，在美国空军战术喷气机上安装加油探头可能是该军种敏捷作战部署战略的一大福音。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe"&gt;正在使用空中加油探测器进行测试的 A-10 疣猪（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 18:20:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthog-being-tested-with-aerial-refueling-probe</guid></item><item><title>我们现在所知道的有关 F-15E WSO 救援行动的一切（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/everything-we-now-know-about-the-operation-to-rescue-the-f-15e-wso</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们获得了许多有关伊朗领土深处的高风险开采工作如何失败的新细节。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/everything-we-now-know-about-the-operation-to-rescue-the-f-15e-wso"&gt;我们现在所知道的关于救援 F-15E WSO 行动的一切（已更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 02:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/everything-we-now-know-about-the-operation-to-rescue-the-f-15e-wso</guid></item><item><title>“萨德”杀伤装置的红外导引头似乎在叙利亚被发现完好无损</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/thaad-kill-vehicles-infrared-seeker-appears-to-have-been-found-in-syria-intact</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从萨德弹道导弹拦截器中回收大部分杀伤车辆可能会造成重大情报损失。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/thaad-kill-vehicles-infrared-seeker-appears-to-have-been-found-in-syria-intact"&gt;萨德杀伤装置的红外导引头似乎在叙利亚被发现完好无损，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 01:50:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/thaad-kill-vehicles-infrared-seeker-appears-to-have-been-found-in-syria-intact</guid></item><item><title>冷战时期的秘密隐形无人机计划预示着 RQ-180 在伊朗可能发挥的作用</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/rq-180s-likely-role-over-iran-foreshadowed-by-secret-cold-war-stealth-drone-program</link><description>&lt;p&gt;几十年前，为了执行非常具体的任务，人们花费了大量资金试图建造一架像 RQ-180 一样的间谍无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/rq-180s-likely-role-over-iran-foreshadowed-by-secret-cold-war-stealth-drone-program"&gt;秘密冷战隐形无人机计划预示着 RQ-180 后在伊朗可能扮演的角色&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 22:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/rq-180s-likely-role-over-iran-foreshadowed-by-secret-cold-war-stealth-drone-program</guid></item><item><title>伊朗深处尘土飞扬的地带如何在数小时内变成美国特种作战基地</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/how-a-dusty-stri-deep-in-iran-can-be-turned-into-a-u-s-special-operations-base-in-hours</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一位前美国空军特种战术中队成员讲述了如何迅速建立和保卫伊朗的临时机场。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/how-a-dusty-stri-deep-in-iran-can-be-turned-into-a-u-s-special-operations-base-in-hours"&gt;《如何在伊朗深处的尘土飞扬的地带在几小时内变成美国特种作战基地》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 18:56:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/how-a-dusty-stri-deep-in-iran-can-be-turned-into-a-u-s-special-operations-base-in-hours</guid></item><item><title>伊朗拒绝停火协议（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-rejects-u-s-ceasefire-deal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着特朗普将伊朗打造成“人间地狱”的最后期限迅速临近，两个敌人之间仍然存在分歧，甚至在暂时暂停战争方面也存在分歧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-rejects-u-s-ceasefire-deal"&gt;伊朗拒绝停火协议（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 17:22:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-rejects-u-s-ceasefire-deal</guid></item><item><title>夜间潜行者 AH-6 小鸟直升机在伊朗前沿着陆点被摧毁</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在作为 F-15E WSO 救援中心的简陋机场的照片中，至少可以看到一架被烧毁的 AH/MH-6 小鸟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran"&gt;在伊朗前沿着陆点被摧毁的夜间追猎者 AH-6 小鸟直升机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 10:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/night-stalker-little-bird-helicopters-destroyed-at-forward-landing-site-in-iran</guid></item><item><title>F-15E 武器系统官员在伊朗被击落已获救（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued</link><description>&lt;p&gt;据报道，经过大规模高风险搜索行动的激烈交火后，这名飞行员被美国特种作战部队救出。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued"&gt;F-15E 武器系统官员在伊朗被击落后已获救（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 10:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-15e-weapon-systems-officer-shot-down-over-iran-has-been-rescued</guid></item></channel></rss>